narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Yes, if you are interested in learning about computational chemistry, take this class.
I would recommend it to a student very interested in computational chemistry or looking for a doable upper level Chem elective
Great class. Very time intensive so take note.
If you need an advanced chemistry class, this is a good one to take. Not too much work, but still interesting.

I would say that this class was a great choice wherein I learned quite a bit about computational chemistry, although the subject is pretty broad, so I didn't get a chance to really delve into a lot of it.
